title: Motorco
description: Motorco Music Hall is an entertainment and events space in Durham, North Carolina. Motorco consists of a large, state of the art Showroom, the Garage Bar and restaurant Parts & Labor with a giant outdoor patio and the Veranda, a covered patio with its own bar and a Parrilla. We have full NC Liquor licenses and have a wide variety of beers, liquors, wines and specialty cocktails (fresh squeezed juices, housemade syrups!). We are located in the Central Park district, within short walking distance to the restaurants and bars of Downtown.

title: Zinchouse
description:
Experience the best of the Triangle winery and brewery good times at ZincHouse, nestled on 87 acres of vineyards and treetop views, offering adults 21+a wide beverage selection of 400+ exquisite wines, our own ZincHouse and local brewery’s craft beers, and a robust offering of bourbon and cigars. The story of our farm and vision continues and grows in 2024!

Open Wednesday – Sunday and featuring live music and food trucks, ZincHouse is the best of good times in the Triangle. See our FAQs.

Step inside one of the three floors of our main building – the ZincHouse. Or sit on the Veranda near the vineyards and take in the beauty, Next door at the beautiful Pavilion, a music stage and the Z-House of Bourbon & Cigar Bar awaits. Two smoking verandas outside the back also feature firepits and the same captivating views. Our Carriage House, nestled in privacy, hosts public dinners, tastings and events.

Our calendar is updated monthly with our live music, food trucks, ticketed events and festivals.
Welcome to ZincHouse. The Triangle areas premier destination.
